  "title": "IT Project Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Define and lead project objectives and plans to deliver IT initiatives on time and within budget, driving cross-functional collaboration and operational excellence. Provide technical support to maintain system performance and ensure reliable data backup and recovery.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Define clear project objectives and develop detailed plans to achieve them within budget constraints</li><li>Manage project timelines, budgets, and status reports to ensure timely delivery and financial control</li><li>Oversee resource allocation, including equipment and personnel, to optimize project execution</li><li>Lead coordination of meetings to align stakeholders on project goals, progress, and risk mitigation</li><li>Implement IT strategies that support project delivery and organizational objectives</li><li>Monitor project progress from initiation to completion, collaborating with internal stakeholders to resolve issues</li><li>Organize and facilitate interdepartmental meetings to drive project alignment and decision-making</li><li>Utilize project management tools to track performance metrics and ensure schedule adherence</li><li>Conduct comprehensive risk assessments and implement effective mitigation strategies to minimize project disruptions</li><li>Perform routine system maintenance, including software updates and security patches, to ensure system reliability</li><li>Troubleshoot hardware and software issues promptly to minimize downtime and support business continuity</li><li>Provide responsive technical support to end-users through help desk tickets, emails, and phone calls</li><li>Assist in implementing and testing data backup procedures to safeguard organizational data</li><li>Maintain accurate documentation of system configurations and technical procedures for knowledge sharing</li><li>Collaborate with IT team members to resolve complex technical issues and improve system performance</li><li>Monitor system performance continuously and ensure effective data backup and recovery processes</li></ul>",
